soon as well..)

A look at the main hall reveals a scene in semi-darkness broken only  by 
the  flickering of hundreds of Amiga,  PC and Commodore 64 screens,  and 
the dominating presence of a twenty foot movie style screen at the front 
of  the  room..  This is used to show continuous films,  animations,  and 
